            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滙豐高管稱公司市值正邁向3000億英鎊",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"滙豐高管稱公司市值正邁向3000億英鎊\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AIwyXUXujIsQ53LRo4A.1A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-10/f97fe2c0-b3f6-11f0-8f96-69b97ee9864c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">滙豐高管稱公司市值正邁向3000億英鎊</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
